---
import Base from "../layouts/base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Founding Member Offer"
  description="Early access to Clarity. Support Plans with added benefits and limited seats"
  type="WebPage"
  canonicalURL="https://getclarity.win/founding-offer"
>
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">Founding Member Offer</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
      A limited opportunity to help shape Clarity. from the inside.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section
    class="mb-24 max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-gray-900 text-white dark:bg-black/50 rounded-lg px-8 py-12 text-center"
  >
    <div class="mb-6 grid md:grid-cols-1 gap-8 text-left md:text-base">
      <div>
        <p class="text-center text-lg">
          We're inviting a small group of early supporters to join Clarity.
          Support Plans before our public launch.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-center text-lg">
          Founding Members will get closer support, early access, and a say in
          how the service evolves.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-center text-lg">
          You'll get priority onboarding, extended async input, and direct
          access to the people behind Clarity.
        </p>
      </div>
      <blockquote
        class="italic text-center mt-6 text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-300"
      >
        “This is your opportunity to shape and influence the support you
        receive.”
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">What Founding Members Get</h2>
  <section
    class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-left mb-24 px-4"
  >
    <div
      class="flex flex-col h-full p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 text-left"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li>Priority onboarding and early session slots</li>
        <li>Extended async support in your first 90 days</li>
        <li>Access to new tools before public release</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div
      class="flex flex-col h-full p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 text-left"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li>Private feedback channel to shape the service</li>
        <li>Locked-in pricing for your first year</li>
        <li>
          Option to remain fully anonymous<br />
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            If you're in a sensitive role or organisation, we can keep your
            identity private. You’ll still get the full experience without being
            named anywhere.
          </span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">What We Ask in Return</h2>
  <section
    class="max-w-xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-1 gap-6 text-center justify-center items-center mb-24 px-4"
  >
    <div
      class="flex flex-col h-full p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 text-left"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li>Willingness to share short feedback at key points</li>
        <li>Input into how Clarity. evolves over time</li>
        <li>Optional testimonial to help build future trust</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-6 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">When It Starts</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      We're onboarding Founding Members in June 2025. <br />
      If you're already on the waitlist, you'll hear from us directly.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="my-16 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center">
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      Want to shape the future of Clarity.?
    </p>
    <a
      href="/#waitlist"
      class="inline-block bg-[#429EDB] text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-[#1F78C1] transition"
    >
      Join the Waitlist
    </a>
  </section>
</Base>
